room_title: Escape room "The Interview" by Twisted Escape Rooms in Lawton
room_address: 201 SW C Ave. Ste. B Lawton, OK 73501
room_description: You receive a letter in the mail, seems an interview has been requested. You've submitted numerous applications, so despite this company looking unfamiliar, you make the appointment anyway. When you arrive, you discover this won't be a typical interview and you'll have 60 min to prove you are qualified for the job... or else!
